        "Description": "CMEs and Coronal Shocks catalogue contains the information of coronal mass ejections (CMEs) related to multi-spacecraft solar energetic particle (SEP) events detected during solar cycle 25. It has been created within the European Union’s Horizon 2020 project SERPENTINE (Solar energetic particle analysis platform for the inner heliosphere). The multi-spacecraft SEP events are documented in the catalogue build during SERPENTINE project",
